title: Helium Scraper v2.4.3.2
description:
Helium Scraper v2.4.3.2

Extract data from any website.
With an intuitive point & click interface.

Choose what to extract with a few clicks.
Just activate selection mode, choose a few sample items and Helium Scraper will deduce the "kind" of item you meant.

Build your extraction rules with intuitive action trees.
Tell Helium Scraper what to do by choosing your actions and placing them into action trees.

Create your own actions.
If more complex actions are needed, extend Helium Scraper's functionality by making use of its JavaScript API.

Export extracted data to a variery of file formats.
Generate CSV or MDB Access database files with the click of a button, or generate XML and custom format files.

Official Website: http://www.heliumscraper.com/en/index.php?p=home
